description:
Here's a preview of our all-new Sweet Treat Patreon bonus episode that finds us Losers teaming up with our fellow Halloweenies to imagine what Stephen King's I, Jason might look like on paper. Want more? Head on over to www.patreon.com/thebarrens and become a Patron for more exclusive bonus content!
